Beautiful gardens greet you at this spacious, comfortable 4 bed, 2 bathroom home located in a quiet court and close to all amenities.

This house has the following features:
* 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and double garage.
* Separate formal lounge, sitting room and large living room.
* Cosy combustion wood fire place in living room
* Open plan meals area leading to modern galley kitchen
* Large covered entertaining area complete with sink and storage. 
* North facing private rear garden.
* Double garage with extra tool room.
* Walk to Vermont South Shopping Centre, Tram 75.
* Short drive to Primary School, The Glen Shopping Centre.
* Cooling and heating supported by split air conditioner. 
* 12 solar panels.


*** COVID19 Update ***
Harcourts remains committed to conducting our services in a safe and responsible manner.
We ask all visitors to please refrain from touching any surfaces, opening cupboards, drawers, windows and doors, when inspecting a property.
If you have symptoms, been in contact with anyone with symptoms or have recently returned from overseas, please do not arrange an inspection.
Thank you for your co-operation.

*** IMPORTANT! REGISTER TO INSPECT PROPERTIES ***
Please register your details and you will be INSTANTLY informed of any updates, changes or cancellations to inspections. Inspection may not proceed without notice if we do not receive any registration.
